# Product Brief: AI Fitness & Meal Planner

**Date:** 2025-11-09
**Author:** BIP
**Context:** greenfield

---

## Executive Summary

The AI Fitness & Meal Planner project aims to develop an AI-driven web platform that provides personalized and adaptive workout and meal plans. It addresses the common challenges of maintaining consistent fitness and nutrition by offering an affordable, unified solution that leverages AI for intelligent planning, weekly adjustments, and progress tracking. The platform will act as a digital personal trainer and nutritionist, empowering users to achieve their health goals through tailored recommendations and continuous adaptation based on their progress and preferences.

---

## Core Vision

### Problem Statement

Many people aim to live healthier lives but struggle to find the time, motivation, or financial resources to maintain consistent fitness routines and balanced nutrition. Existing fitness and meal apps often provide generic content or require costly subscriptions for personalization. This project seeks to create an AI-driven web platform that intelligently combines workout and meal planning into a unified experience. By leveraging AI personalization, weekly replanning, and user-specific progress tracking, the platform will act as a digital personal trainer and nutritionist â€” simple, affordable, and adaptive. The objective of this project is to develop a comprehensive, AI-assisted web application that automatically generates and adjusts personalized workout and meal plans. Users will receive tailored recommendations based on their fitness goals (e.g., stronger legs, better endurance, weight loss), preferences, and progress over time. The system will enable users to log results, replan weekly, and visualize their improvement, promoting long-term health habits and consistency.

